DataElement.preferredName: Person Identifier Transplant Registry Unified Management Program Number
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A person's Transplant Registry Unified Management Program identifier number, a Japanese centralized, computer-based software suite developed to manage hematopoietic stem cell transplant outcome data offline in transplant centers. The system emphasizes convenience to institutes, safety of patient information, quality of data management, and outcomes of transplantations.
